    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;evocation&nbsp;[fire, good, light];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;bard 4, cleric/oracle 4, hunter 4, magus 4, paladin 4, ranger 4;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S, DF<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;personal<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;you<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 round/level<br>\n    \n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You create a disk of sunlight on one arm. Any creature that strikes you with a melee attack deals normal damage, but also takes 1d6 points of fire damage + 1 point per caster level (maximum +15). Creatures with reach weapons are not subject to this damage if they attack you. The shield provides illumination as if it were a <i>continual flame</i> spell. You can only have one instance of this spell in effect at a time. It does not stack with similar damaging aura spells such as <i>fire shield</i>.</p>\n</div>\n",
